Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.27,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Animal!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the theme for this installment is animals!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't work with the gimmick.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We gave up on that!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, we have a new member!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather sudden.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pam-pa-pa-pam!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Lucoa doing here?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough material \Nwith just three of us.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So blunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.54,0:00:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we've decided \Nto introduce Lucoa as a regular!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(21,354,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Cat!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.05,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.90,0:00:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow-meow!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's kinda cute!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow-meow-meow!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.18,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucoa, your "cat" is pretty half-baked...{revisit}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.85,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.27,0:00:51.03,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Meow, meow, meow, meow.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.27,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.99,0:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You puked?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cats will be cats.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.03,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Does our audience want to see this?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.24,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(29,362,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Bear!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearie-bear!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty good, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.25,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bearie-bearie-bear!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucoa, you haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all bear.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just ears!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot something!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that necessary?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's alive?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even see your face.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ahh!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Sea Otter!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a single trace of sea otter.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, I do. See?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the clamshells.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No otter is like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, holding hands! How cute!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These just won't open, will they?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some perseverance!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Bunny!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.25,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really an animal.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Dragon!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just redundant!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Koala!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This one... could work.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Lucoa?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Dairy Cow!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,20,,Your boobs are completely exposed.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,20,,They are not. This is body paint.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest her.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My time is up already?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, we've completed our quota for this installment.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Quota?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, don't miss our next {\i1}Dragon Something{\i0}!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've already had enough...
Comment: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Presenting a New Member"